<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="56" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="7.[174,1377,2138,3111]" pageId="7" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[177,529,2885,2914]" pageId="7" pageNumber="56">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix II. The conservation status of the Gerp’s Mouse 
<taxonomicName box="[278,373,2924,2953]" class="Mammalia" family="Lemuridae" genus="Lemur" kingdom="Animalia" order="Primates" pageId="7" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Lemur</taxonomicName>
has not yet been assessed on The IUCN Red List. However, assessed as critically endangered at the IUCN/SSC 
<taxonomicName authority="Red-Listing Workshop" authorityName="Red-Listing Workshop" box="[699,1116,2959,2992]" class="Mammalia" family="Lemuridae" genus="Lemur" kingdom="Animalia" order="Primates" pageId="7" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Lemur Red-Listing Workshop</taxonomicName>
held in July 2012. This species is not known to occur in any protected area. It is threatened by very high rates of deforestation in Madagascar’s eastern lowland rainforests.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
